This repository contains tests with:
- rest-assured framework
- TestNG
To run tests you need JDK 11.

tests for calculator Test cases are here
 - https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jhCeoXurJMMd8zc9I0AdeEecHJm55R6J2NDw8mdPCVY/edit#gid=0

Dependencies for Maven project:
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.rest-assured</groupId>
    <artifactId>rest-assured</artifactId>
    <version>4.3.0</version>
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>
To run tests with TestNG add:
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.testng</groupId>
    <artifactId>testng</artifactId>
    <version>6.14.3</version>
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>

We can send a GET call to http://localhost:8080/calc.
All operations are made one by one, only integers are accepted, "/" is necessary to divide values.
Example: http://localhost:8080/calc/+1/-2/*5 = -5.

